1. Ja sam potrošio novac na hranu. (*potrošio*) (I spent money on food.)
2. Ona će potrošiti celu platu na novi telefon. (*potrošiti*) (She will spend her whole salary on a new phone.)
3. Ti si potrošio previše vremena na to. (*potrošio*) (You have spent too much time on that.)
4. Oni su potrošili svu energiju na utakmici. (*potrošili*) (They spent all their energy during the game.)
5. Kada bih znao da će se to dogoditi, ne bih potrošio toliko novca. (*potrošio*) (If I knew that was going to happen, I wouldn't have spent so much money.)
6. Koliko si novca potrošio za praznike? (*potrošio*) (How much money did you spend for the holidays?)
7. Nećeš moći da potrošiš sve te knjige do kraja meseca. (*potrošiš*) (You won't be able to read all those books by the end of the month.)
8. Moja sestra je potrošila sve svoje prihrane u školi. (*potrošila*) (My sister spent all her allowance at school.)
9. Oni nisu znali da će potrošiti toliko goriva na putu. (*potrošiti*) (They didn't know they would spend so much fuel on the road.)
10. Molim te, nemoj potrošiti sav novac na odeću. (*potrošiti*) (Please don't spend all your money on clothes.)